ren>feature<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space>try:<lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#logMessage<openparen><apos>s3FileUploadACL<space>===========================================================================<apos><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>parameterReceived<space>=<space>eval<openparen>feature.getAttribute<openparen><apos>_Execution_Parameters<apos><closeparen>.replace<openparen><apos><backslash>n<apos><comma><space><apos><apos><closeparen><closeparen><lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#<space>AWS<space>IAM<space>Role<space>ARN<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>iam_role<space>=<space>feature.getAttribute<openparen>parameterReceived<openbracket><apos>iam_role<apos><closebracket><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#<space>Full<space>path<space><openparen>key<closeparen><space>of<space>the<space>file<space>to<space>upload<space>in<space>S3<space>bucket<space><openparen>prefix<solidus>file<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>ftp_path<space>=<space>feature.getAttribute<openparen>parameterReceived<openbracket><apos>ftp_path<apos><closebracket><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#<space>Full<space>path<space>of<space>the<space>file<space>on<space>FME<space>Server<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>fme_server_path<space>=<space>feature.getAttribute<openparen>parameterReceived<openbracket><apos>fme_server_path<apos><closebracket><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#<space>S3<space>bucket<space>name<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>s3_ftp_bucket<space>=<space>feature.getAttribute<openparen>parameterReceived<openbracket><apos>s3_ftp_bucket<apos><closebracket><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#S3<space>bucket<space>Owner<space>Account<space>ID<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>bucket_owner_id<space>=<space>feature.getAttribute<openparen>parameterReceived<openbracket><apos>bucket_owner_id<apos><closebracket><closeparen><lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#<space>Connect<space>to<space>FTP<space>S3<space>Bucket<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>s3<space>=<space>connectToS3<openparen>feature<comma><space>iam_role<closeparen><lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#<space>Upload<space>file<space>S3<space>Bucket<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>s3.Bucket<openparen>s3_ftp_bucket<closeparen>.upload_file<openparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>fme_server_path<comma><space>ftp_path<comma><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>ExtraArgs=<opencurly><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><apos>GrantFullControl<apos>:<space><apos>id=<apos><space>+<space>bucket_owner_id<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><closecurly><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><closeparen><lf><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setAttribute<openparen><quote>Execution.status<quote><comma><space>0<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>#logMessage<openparen><apos><gt><gt><gt><space>Execution.status<space>=<space>0<apos><closeparen><lf><lf><space><space><space><space>except:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>raise<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setAttribute<openparen><quote>Execution.status<quote><comma><space>0<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space> }    PY_OUTPUT_TAGS { PYOUTPUT <Rejected> }    OUTPUT { PYOUTPUT FEATURE_TYPE PythonCaller_2_OUTPUT         }    OUTPUT { <Rejected> FEATURE_TYPE PythonCaller_2_<Rejected>         }
